They also help us and carefully-considered third parties understand the performance of our marketing activities and improve the relevance of the adverts that you see. These uses of personal data and technologies are used by us or our carefully-considered third parties, and may involve the use and sharing of personal data (such as your transaction data, or account details e.g. email address and telephone number).
